            <thetext>Here are the steps for reproducing the bug:

1) Press the Add button, until a vertical scroll bar is needed.  None appears.

2) Reload the page.  Press the scenario 2 button.  Press the Add button, until a vertical scroll bar is needed.  It appears. We have increased the height a little.

3) Reload the page.  Press the scenario 3 button.  Press the Add button, until a vertical scroll bar is needed.  It appears, but the cell at bottom left corner isn&#39;t painted.  We have increased the width a little.

Conclusion: vertical scroll bar appears or not depending on the width and height, even if it has enough room.</thetext>
